# рҹҰҜ Smart Path Suggestor вҖ” Complete Code Walkthrough

> **Purpose**: A real-time navigation assistant for visually impaired users. It uses a phone's camera to detect obstacles, estimates their distance, and provides **voice guidance + vibration alerts** to suggest the safest walking path.

---

## рҹ“Ғ Project Structure

| File | Role | Lines |
|------|------|-------|
| [server.py](file:///d:/Project/Smart%20Path%20Suggestor/server.py) | Flask API server вҖ” receives frames, runs AI models, returns results | 361 |
| [navigation_engine.py](file:///d:/Project/Smart%20Path%20Suggestor/navigation_engine.py) | Navigation brain вҖ” tracking, smoothing, voice messages, alerts | 516 |
| [mobile_client.html](file:///d:/Project/Smart%20Path%20Suggestor/mobile_client.html) | Mobile web app вҖ” camera capture, voice output, vibration | 672 |
| [detection_local.py](file:///d:/Project/Smart%20Path%20Suggestor/detection_local.py) | Standalone local mode вҖ” runs everything on laptop with webcam | 131 |
| [gen_cert.py](file:///d:/Project/Smart%20Path%20Suggestor/gen_cert.py) | SSL certificate generator for HTTPS (optional) | 45 |
| [yolov8n.pt](file:///d:/Project/Smart%20Path%20Suggestor/yolov8n.pt) | Pre-trained YOLOv8 nano model weights | вҖ” |

