## рҹ”‘ Tech Stack

| Technology | Purpose |
|------------|---------|
| **Python + Flask** | HTTP API server |
| **YOLOv8** (Ultralytics) | Real-time object detection (80 COCO classes) |
| **MiDaS** (Intel) | Monocular depth estimation from single image |
| **OpenCV** | Image processing (decode, resize, color conversion) |
| **PyTorch** | Deep learning inference runtime |
| **Web Speech API** | Text-to-speech on mobile browser |
| **Vibration API** | Haptic feedback on mobile browser |
| **Canvas API** | Frame capture from video stream |
